rFishStatus

Installation

You can install the development version of rFishStatus from GitHub using the devtools package:

install.packages("devtools")

devtools::install_github("thomazfabrin/rFishStatus")

Reporting Bugs or Issues

If you encounter any bugs or have suggestions for improvements while using rFishStatus, please feel free to open an issue on the GitHub repository.
